snippet.textDisplay:
Yath duniyahas manz chene Kashiris kune cheez seeth tarawath evaan bas paney zabaane hend ze lafaz bozeth tche Kasheer te Mehjoor yaad pewaan.
Wherever it is, it is just comforting to listen to the songs of our land. This language has kept us who we are. We have composed the words of resistance into beautiful melodies in this language. Whether they are sung in Pakistan or anywhere. Still kudos to Coke studio bey panen Kasheren Kakan Salaam.
